18:
But Yahweh wants to act kindly toward you;\q2 he is great because he desires to act mercifully.
\q1 Do not forget he is a God who acts justly;
\q2 Yahweh is pleased with those who patiently trust in him.

28:
His breath is like a flood that covers his enemies up to their necks.\q2 He will separate the nations in order to destroy some of them;
\q2 it is as though he will put horses' bridles on them so he can lead them away to destruction.


